[6] EPIC 1996 Crypto Sourcebook Now Available
=======================================================================

Copies of the EPIC 1996 Cryptography and Privacy Sourcebook are now
available for $25 each. The 1996 EPIC Sourcebook is an all new compilation
of the key documents of the last year including the latest internal
FBI/NSA/White House documents obtained under the Freedom of Information
Act, bills, analysis, and more on cryptography, wiretapping, and export
controls. A limited number of 1995 sourcebooks are also available for $25.

For more information, visit the EPIC Bookstore at

   http://www.epic.org/epic/bookstore.html


