    <h1>[3365] <a href="dl?thread=Re:+Your+attention+please....+(fwd)&after=3365">Re: Your attention please.... (fwd)</a></h1>
    <h2><i>Bob Chatelle &lt;kip@world.std.com&gt;</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>: Re: Your attention please.... (fwd)
<b>To</b>: Michael Loomis &lt;ml3e+@andrew.cmu.edu&gt;
