    <h1>[3385] <a href="dl?thread=Waiting+Game+on+wiretapping+and+crypto,+from+HotWired&after=3385">Waiting Game on wiretapping and crypto, from HotWired</a></h1>
    <h2><i>Declan McCullagh &lt;declan@well.com&gt;</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>: Waiting Game on wiretapping and crypto, from HotWired
<b>To</b>: fight-censorship@vorlon.mit.edu
<b>From</b>: Declan McCullagh &lt;declan@well.com&gt;
