    <h1>[3370] <a href="dl?thread=More+on+the+latest+Surveillance+Bill...&after=3370">More on the latest Surveillance Bill...</a></h1>
    <h2><i>jseiger@cdt.org (Jonah Seiger)</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>: More on the latest Surveillance Bill...
<b>To</b>: fight-censorship+@andrew.cmu.edu, action@eff.org,
         internet_censorship@monad.net
<b>From</b>: jseiger@cdt.org (Jonah Seiger)
