The University of Nebraska is threatening web pages that have the word
"Husker" in their title, according to the message attached below. Guess
they'll have to go after these sites too:

       Husker Power web site
       Asger Schnack: Jeg Husker Alt
       (AP) Husker QB Brook Berringer killed in plane crash near NU campus
       Husker Du
       Penstemon 'Husker Red' is 1996 Perennial Plant of the Year
       Husker midwestern home design
       Joel's Husker Page

I've set up a web page at http://www.well.com/~declan/huskers.html and
registered the URL with AltaVista and HotBot. It's called: "Husker web
pages, the University of Nebraska, and braindead policies."

I wonder what the university will do, if anything? This message is copied
to some University of Nebraska administrators and faculty members.
Redistribute freely.

-Declan

