    <h1>[3369] <a href="dl?thread=URGENT:+Surveillance+Bill+Gets+New+Life+-+House+Vote+lLikely+TODAY!&after=3369">URGENT: Surveillance Bill Gets New Life - House Vote lLikely TODAY!</a></h1>
    <h2><i>jseiger@cdt.org (Jonah Seiger)</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>: URGENT: Surveillance Bill Gets New Life - House Vote lLikely TODAY!
