    <h1>[3371] <a href="dl?thread=Schumer:+%22Smokescreen+Called+Privacy%22&after=3371">Schumer: "Smokescreen Called Privacy"</a></h1>
    <h2><i>telstar@wired.com (--Todd Lappin--&gt;)</i></h2>
    <pre>
<b>Subject</b>: Schumer: "Smokescreen Called Privacy"
<b>To</b>: fight-censorship@vorlon.mit.edu
