&gt; 
&gt; Two prime examples of site with PHOTOS  containng male frontal nudity on
&gt; GeoCities are:
&gt; 
&gt; Rob's Bound & Gagged
&gt; http://www.geocities.com/WestHollywood/3100
&gt; 
&gt; contains graphic photos of sadomaochism showing male genetalia
&gt; 
&gt; Nude Celebrities
&gt; http://www.geocities.com/WestHollywood/3102
&gt; 
&gt; My site only contained abstract pencil drawings with no sexual activity
&gt; portrayed.
&gt; 
&gt; There are dozens of sites containing nudity on GeoCities and obviously
&gt; something else is going on here.

Yes, but it's not necessarily something sinister.  From the evidence
I've seen GeoCities is just responding to the "squeaky wheels."  When
a page gets a pile of hits they check it out.  I'm not especially
impressed with the actions they're taking, but I doubt there's any
plot to stifle free thinking on the net.

  -- Dave

</pre>

