Notice of Public Hearing

The Tacoma City Council will conduct a public hearing on Tuesday,
August 27, 1996, at approximately 6:00 p.m. relative to City taxation of
Internet access providers.

This public hearing will take place in the City Council Chambers on
the first floor of the Tacoma Municipal Building, 747 Market Street, Tacoma,
Washington.  All persons will have an opportunity to present their comments
at the meeting.  For further information, please contact Duston Jensen at 
591-5247.

The City of Tacoma does not discriminate on the basis of disabilities in any
of its programs or services.  Special accommodations can be provided upon
request, prior to the meeting.  To arrange for these accommodations please
contact the City Clerk's office at 591-5171 (voice) or dial 591-5058 (TDD).

Rick Rosenbladt
City Clerk

Resolution No. 33474
Adopted August 6, 1996


