<h2>How to Order</h2>
<p>All material can be purchased through C.O.S.E. inc. However, as far as the 714X is concerned 
in Canada, the patient must have his/her doctor <a href="ti02imga.htm">apply for an authorization</a> at the Health 
Protection Branch (HPB) in Ottawa. </p>
<p>Please note that the office is open Monday thru Friday, 8h30 to 12h00, 13h30 to 17h00 (E.S.T.). 
We can be reached by phone at (819) 564-7883 or by fax at (819) 564-4668.</p>
<hr>
