<CENTER><STRONG>
<A HREF="http://www.christophers.com/dining.jpg"><EM>Christopher's</EM> formal
dining room</A>, the ultimate in dining elegance, features classical yet
innovative French cuisine.  <EM>Christopher's</EM> has been inducted into the
Fine Dining Hall of Fame, honored by the Mobil Travel Guide as a four-star
selection, been chosen by critic Mimi Sheraton as one of the top 50 restaurants
in the U.S.A. and been selected as one of the top 50 restaurants in the U.S.A. 
by the Conde Nast Reader's poll.
</STRONG></CENTER> 
<P>
</P>
<CENTER>
<STRONG><EM>Christopher's</EM> formal dining room is open Tuesday through
Sunday, from 6:00 PM for dinner. Seating at Christopher's is limited to 80
inside and 40 on the private patio. Gentlemen guests are required to wear
jackets.
</STRONG></CENTER> 
<P></P>
