<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>The Wine and Cigar Club </TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="cigarbck.jpg" BGCOLOR="#ffffff">

<CENTER><IMG SRC="Cigar.gif" ALIGN="BOTTOM" WIDTH="135" HEIGHT="185"></CENTER>

<CENTER><H2><I>Christopher's Wine and Cigar Club</I></H2></CENTER>

<CENTER>
<P><STRONG>Located above <EM>Christopher's</EM> landmark restaurant
is a one of a kind facility devoted to the art of fine wines and great cigars.
Members and their guests avail themselves of this exclusive atmosphere daily for
lunch and wine tastings from thier private lockers or humidors in addition to
the private dining room which may accomodate up to 48.</STRONG></P>

<P><STRONG><EM>Christopher's</EM> is pleased to make memberships in this unparalleled
facility available for our special friends. We are so very pleased with the evolution of
the club, in particular its richly appointed decor and elegant ambiance. This unique
facility offers a new arena for lovers of fine wines and great cigars. Club membership
affords members unlimited opportunities with regard to business and personal
pursuits.</STRONG></P>
</CENTER>

<P><BR></P>

