<CENTER>
<H1>Wine List Highlights</H1>
</CENTER>    
<CENTER>
<P><STRONG><A HREF="chrisbio.html">Christopher</A> and <A HREF="paola.html">Paola</A>
Gross are industry leaders in bringing hard to find wines to Arizona. The wine cellar
contains close to 850 different labels with over half a million dollars invested
in inventory.  Eighty wines by the glass are available and are expertly paired
with menu selections by Paola Gross.  All of the <EM>Christopher's</EM> by the
glass wines are available to purchase from <EM>Christopher's Cellar</EM>, a
salon style retail wine shop.  Customers are invited to taste before they buy.</STRONG></P>
</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<P><STRONG><EM>Christopher's</EM> and <EM>Christopher's Bistro</EM> are
nationally recognized for their extensive wine list. Selected as winner of The
Wine Spectator Award of Excellence for 1991, 1992 and 1993 the list at <EM>Christopher's</EM>
offers a vast collection of wines and spirits from around the world with a focus
on French regionals and California's finest. Christopher Gross, or Paola Gross,
<EM>Christopher's</EM> Wine Director, will gladly provide their expert
assistance matching wines and particular dishes. </STRONG>
</P>
</CENTER>
<CENTER>
<P><STRONG><EM>Christopher's Wine Shop</EM>, at <EM>Christopher's Bistro</EM>,
offers a fully stocked, temperature controlled retail wine shop with competitive
pricing. In our &quot;salon - type&quot; atmosphere, one may taste the wine
prior to purchasing.  Enjoy a glass of wine at our bar from the list of over 80
wines by the glass ranging from $3 - $28 per glass. Our highly trained wine and
food specialists are available to assist you with advice on stocking your cellar
and tracking those esoteric and hard-to-find wines.</STRONG></P>
</CENTER> 
<P><FONT SIZE="-1">PLEASE NOTE : CHRISTOPHER'S RESERVES THE RIGHT TO ADJUST
INVENTORY DUE TO AVAILABILITY.</FONT></P>
<P></P> 
