<HEAD>
   <TITLE>The Wine and Cigar Club Membership</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" BACKGROUND="cigarbck.jpg">

<CENTER>
<P><IMG SRC="Cigar.gif" HEIGHT=185 WIDTH=135 ALIGN=BOTTOM></P>
<H1><I>
Christopher's Wine and Cigar Club<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+0>(LIMITED NUMBER OF MEMBERSHIPS AVAILABLE)</FONT><BR>
</I></H1>
</CENTER>

<P><BR></P>

<H3>Annual Memberships Include:</H3>

<UL><UL>

<LI><B>use of private humidor</B></LI>

<LI><B>wine storage (limited number of private wine cellars available)</B></LI>

<LI><B>selected wines by the bottle @ cost plus 20%</B></LI>

<LI><B>cigars by the box @ cost plus 20%</B></LI>

<LI><B>NEW...Christopher's charge card for use at: Christopher's, the Bistro
&amp; the Club</B></LI>

<LI><B>engraved V.I.P. brass name plate</B></LI>

<LI><B>unlimited usage of the Cigar Room</B></LI>

