http://www.christophers.com:80/ciglovers.html 204.238.118.11 19970121004013 text/html 12659
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Enterprise/2.0a
Date: Tue, 21 Jan 1997 00:40:09 GMT
