<HEAD>
   <TITLE>Christopher's Recipes: Bistro Herb Flavored Oil for Broiling</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#800040" BGCOLOR="#FFFF80" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#8000FF" ALINK="#FF8000" BACKGROUND="chrisbg.jpg">

<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="recipe.gif" ALT="Christopher's Recipe" HEIGHT=60 WIDTH=166></P></CENTER>

<H1>BISTRO HERB FLAVORED OIL FOR BROILING</H1>

<H2><IMG SRC="circ.gif" HEIGHT=34 WIDTH=40 ALIGN=CENTER>INGREDIENTS</H2>

<UL>
<LI>7 1/4 cups Olive Oil</LI>
<LI>6 1/2 cups fresh Rosemary leaves</LI>
<LI>2 1/4 cup fresh Basil</LI>
<LI>1/2 cup fresh Garlic</LI>
<LI>5 3/4 cup fresh Cilantro</LI>
<LI>1 cup Pine Nuts</LI>
<LI>2 1/2 cup Parmesan cheese</LI>
<LI>1/4 cup Salt</LI>
<LI>3 1/2 cup Cracked Black Pepper</LI>
</UL>

<H2><IMG SRC="circ.gif" HEIGHT=34 WIDTH=40 ALIGN=CENTER>PREPARATION</H2>

<OL>
<P>Pur&eacute;e eveything but Salt, Pepper and Olive Oil in blender.</P>
<P>Slowly drizzle in Olive Oil to emulsify Pesto</P>
<P>Add Cracked Black Pepper and Salt to taste</P>
</OL>

