<HEAD>
   <TITLE>Christopher's Recipes: Granit&eacute;</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#800040" BGCOLOR="#FFFF80" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#8000FF" ALINK="#FF8000" BACKGROUND="chrisbg.jpg">

<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="recipe.gif" ALT="Christopher's Recipe" HEIGHT=60 WIDTH=166></P></CENTER>

<H1>GRANIT&Eacute;</H1>

<H2><IMG SRC="circ.gif" HEIGHT=34 WIDTH=40 ALIGN=CENTER>INGREDIENTS</H2>

<UL>
<LI>One Quart of any fresh fruit juice</LI>

<LI>6 oz sugar</LI>
</UL>

<H2><IMG SRC="circ.gif" HEIGHT=34 WIDTH=40 ALIGN=CENTER>PREPARATION</H2>

<OL>
<P>Mix ingredients and place in container</P>

<P>Place container in freezer</P>

<P><B>When frozen scrape with a spoon and serve</B></P>

<P>If using champagne or red wine add 2/3 bottle of water and to the champagne
the juice of one lemon</P>

<P>750 ml wine = 1 bottle</P>

<P>3/4 bottle water</P>

<P>1 lemon if using champagne </P>
</OL>

