<HEAD>
   <TITLE>Christopher's Recipes: Walnut and Ni&ccedil;oise Olive Rustic Bread</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#800040" BGCOLOR="#FFFF80" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#8000FF" ALINK="#FF8000" BACKGROUND="chrisbg.jpg">

<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="recipe.gif" ALT="Christopher's Recipe" HEIGHT=60 WIDTH=166></P></CENTER>

<H1>WALNUT &amp; NI&Ccedil;OISE OLIVE RUSTIC BREAD</H1>

<H2><IMG SRC="circ.gif" HEIGHT=34 WIDTH=40 ALIGN=TEXTTOP>INGREDIENTS</H2>

<UL>
<LI><B>5 cups whole wheat flour</B></LI>
<LI><B>2<SUP><FONT SIZE=-2>1/4</FONT></SUP> cups high bulten</B></LI>
<LI><B>7 cups all purpose flour</B></LI>
<LI><B><FONT SIZE=-1>1/2</FONT> cup yeast</B></LI>
<LI><B>2<SUP><FONT SIZE=-2>1/2</FONT></SUP> quarts warm water</B></LI>
<LI><B><FONT SIZE=-1>3/4</FONT> cups honey</B></LI>
<LI><B><FONT SIZE=-1>3/4</FONT> cups ni&ccedil;oise olive pur&eacute;e</B></LI>
<LI><B>4 tbls. salt</B></LI>
<LI><B>4<SUP><FONT SIZE=-2>1/2</FONT></SUP> cups chopped walnuts</B></LI>
<LI><B>2 rough chopped ni&ccedil;oise olives</B></LI>
</UL>

<H2><IMG SRC="circ.gif" HEIGHT=34 WIDTH=40 ALIGN=TEXTTOP>PREPARATION</H2>

<UL>
<UL TYPE=SQUARE>
<LI><B>Mix all ingredients, shape the dough, let rise.</B></LI>
<LI><B>Bake at 350 degrees for 20 minutes.</B></LI>
</UL>
</UL>

