<HTML>
<HEAD>
   <TITLE>Christopher's Recipes: Perfect Pizza Dough</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY TEXT="#800040" BGCOLOR="#FFFF80" LINK="#0000FF" VLINK="#8000FF" ALINK="#FF8000" BACKGROUND="chrisbg.jpg">

<CENTER><P><IMG SRC="recipe.gif" ALT="Christopher's Recipe" HEIGHT=60 WIDTH=166></P></CENTER>

<H1>THE PERFECT PIZZA DOUGH<BR>
</H1>

<H2><IMG SRC="circ.gif" HEIGHT=34 WIDTH=40 ALIGN=TEXTTOP>INGREDIENTS</H2>

<UL>
<LI><B>24 oz water</B></LI>

<LI><B><FONT SIZE=-1>3/4</FONT> oz fresh yeast</B></LI>

<LI><B><FONT SIZE=-1>3/4</FONT> oz sugar</B></LI>

<LI><B><FONT SIZE=-1>3/4</FONT> lb all purpose flour</B></LI>

<LI><B>1 tbls salt</B></LI>

<LI><B>3 <FONT SIZE=-1>1/2</FONT> oz extra virgin olive oil</B></LI>

<LI><B>1 <FONT SIZE=-1>1/2</FONT> fresh chopped thyme</B></LI>
</UL>

<H2><IMG SRC="circ.gif" HEIGHT=34 WIDTH=40 ALIGN=TEXTTOP>PREPARATION</H2>

<UL>
<UL TYPE=SQUARE>
<LI><B>Combine yeast &amp; water in mixing bowl</B></LI>

<LI><B>Add the remaining ingredients in mixer</B></LI>

<LI><B>Mix for 10 minutes</B></LI>

<LI><B>Scale dough &amp; make 6 oz balls</B></LI>

<LI><B>Cover &amp; let rest until dough doubles in size</B></LI>

<LI><B>Dough is now ready to work with</B></LI>
</UL>
</UL>

<P><BR>
</P>

<P><B>Back to <A HREF="http://www.christophers.com/">Christopher's Web
Site</A></B></P>

<P><B><I><FONT SIZE=-1>designed and hosted by <A HREF="http://www.grouper.com/">Grouper
Technologies</A></FONT></I></B></P>

