<TITLE>J. (Bob) Balaram's publications</TITLE>

<H2>Publications</H2>
<H4>
Some of these technical reports and papers are available online
subject to copyright related restrictions. 

<P>
<HR>
<H3>
<blockquote> 

J. A. Cutts, K. T. Nock, J. A. Jones, G. Rodriguez and J. Balaram, 
"Planetary Exploration by Robotic AeroVehicles",
to appear in journal Autonomous Robots issue entitled "Autonomous Vehicles for
Planetary Exploration".
<P>

J. A. Cutts, K. T. Nock, J. A. Jones, G. Rodriguez, J. Balaram, G. E. Powell
and S. P. Synnot, "Aerovehicles for  Planetary Exploration", 
1995 IEEE Conference on Robotics & Automation, Nagoya, Japan, May 1995.

<P>

J. Balaram, S. Hayati, and R. Volpe. "Multi-Sensor Inspection Telerobot."
In Proceedings of the 1994 International Symposium on Robotics and
Automation (ISRAM '94), Maui Hawaii, August 1994.
<A HREF="papers/isram94.ps.gz">postscript</A> (4 pages, 1.3M)<p>

R. Volpe and J. Balaram.  "Technology for Robotic Surface Inspection
in Space".  In AIAA Conference on Intelligent Robots in Field,
Factory, Service, and Space (CIRFFSS '94), Houston, Texas, March
20-24, 1994.
<A HREF="papers/cirffss.ps.gz">postscript</A> (11 pages, 900K)
<P>

J. Balaram. "Automated Visual Change Detection for Remote 
Surface Inspection", JPL Engineering Memo 3474-93-004.
<P>

J. Balaram and S. Hayati, "Telerobotic Inspection For Remote Space 
Platforms". In Proceedings of the ESA/INRIA Workshop on Computer Vision 
for Space Applications, Antibes, France, September 1993. 
<P> 

 
S. Hayati, J. Balaram, et-al, "Remote Surface Inspection System", 
In Robotics, Vol 11-1, May 1993. 
<P> 

K. V. Prasad and J. Balaram, "Automated Inspection For Remote Telerobotic 
Operations", In Proceedings of the IEEE Conference on Robotics & Automation, 
Atlanta, Ga. May 1993. 
<P> 

J. Balaram and S. Hayati, "A Supervisory Telerobotics Testbed for 
Unstructured Environments", Journal of Robotic Systems, 1992. 
<P>

J. Balaram and H. Stone, "Automated Assembly in the JPL Telerobot Testbed", 
in the book Intelligent Robotic Systems for Space Exploration, Chapter 8, 
pp.297-342, Kluwer Academic Publishers, Norwell, MA, 1992. 
<P> 

H. Stone, J. Balaram and J. Beahan, "Experiences with the JPL Telerobot 
Testbed: Issues and Insights", NASA Workshop on Space
Telerobotics, Pasadena, CA, 1989.
<P>
 
J. Balaram, "Probabilistic Methods for Robot Motion Determination", 
In Proceedings of the SPIE Symposium on Advances in Intelligent Robotics 
Systems, Cambridge, MA, 1988.
<P> 
 
J. Balaram, G. Rodriguez and J. Beahan, "A Run-Time Control Architecture 
for the JPL Telerobot", In Proceedings of the IEEE Robotics and Automation
Conference, Raleigh, North Carolina. 
<P>

G. N. Saridis and J. Balaram  "Suboptimal Control for Nonlinear Systems", 
in Control-Theory and Advanced Technology, Vol.2, No.3, pp.547-562, 1986. 
<P>

J. Balaram and G.N. Saridis, "Suboptimal Control of Nonlinear Systems", 
In Proceedings IEEE Conference on Decision and Control, 
Ft. Lauderdale, December, 1985.
<P>

J. Balaram, C. Shen, R. T. Lahey Jr. and M. Becker, "An Analysis of 
Boiling Water Nuclear Reactor Stability", US Nuclear Regulatory Commission 
Report, NUREG/CR-3291, May 1983. 
