<TITLE>Long Range Science Rover Technology</TITLE>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#8f8fff" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#00ff00" VLINK="#0000ff">

<H1> Long Range Science Rover <br>
Operator Interface
<p>

<p><hr><p>

<h4>

<ul>
<li> <a href=
"http://robotics.jpl.nasa.gov/tasks/scirover/operator/wits/homepage.html"> 
Web Interface for Telescience (WITS) 
     --- Public Version </a> <br>
WITS is the RoCS interface for scientists to use over the web from their 
home institutions to view downlink data and submit commands for the rover. 
This interface is also available to the public with the limitation that
the public version cannot command the real rover.
</ul>
