<LI>Develop detail plans for Long-Range Science Rover task
<LI>Design and build new joints for steering and the manipulator
arm
<LI>Develop initial WEB-based operator interface
<LI>Design and begin implementation for an on-board command interpreter
<LI>Start the development of autonomous science instrument pointing
and sampling with positive verification algorithms <BR>

</OL>

