This report describes the progress made during the second fiscal 
quarter of FY 1996
(from December 18, 1995 to March 17, 1996) and the plans for the next quarter 
in the JPL Telerobotics program.<P>

The JPL Telerobotics program is organized into three work elements with a
varying number of tasks for each:<P>

