<DOCNO>WT04-B21-106</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA044-000798-B004-74</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://robotics.jpl.nasa.gov:80/tasks/scirover/technology/spectrometer/homepage.html 128.149.37.4 19970118120245 text/html 2731
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 18 Jan 1997 12:02:39 GMT
