<P>

R. Volpe and P. Khosla. "Analysis and Experimental Verification 
of a Fourth Order Plant Model for Manipulator Force Control".
Robotics and Automation Magazine, 1(2), June 1994.
<A HREF="Jmodel.ps.gz">postscript</A> (22 pages, 690K) <P>

