http://robotics.jpl.nasa.gov:80/tasks/steler/accomplishments/fy92/ksc/ksc-inspection.html 128.149.37.4 19970118114540 text/html 3299
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Sat, 18 Jan 1997 11:45:20 GMT
